[genericglass Cocktail] Serving Glass: Cocktail Chilled

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
1 oz [genericingredient Scotch] Glenlivet Scotch Whiskey
1/2 oz Dry Vermouth
1/2 tsp [genericingredient Triple Sec] Hiram Walker Triple Sec
1 TBSP [genericingredient Orange Juice] Orange Juice
1/3 tsp Powder Sugar
Shake and Strain
Garnish: Lemon Twist

